e20-co225-Denture-Design-Studio.title: Denture Design Studio
e20-co225-Denture-Design-Studio.description: A graphical platform that provides an opportunity for real-time denture designing with features for self evaluation for dental students with guidance from assessors

e20-co225-Erasmus-plus-Project-Web-and-M.title: Erasmus plus Project Web and MIS
e20-co225-Erasmus-plus-Project-Web-and-M.description: This is a comprehensive software solution designed to support the management and coordination of Erasmus+ projects. It serves as a centralized platform for stakeholders involved in Erasmus+ projects to collaborate, track progress, manage documents, and facilitate communication.
